testcase.name: ProductService should invoke get products endpoint
ProductService should handle errors on get products endpoint
ProductService should handle errors on get bids endpoint
BidViewerComponent should get list of bids
BidViewerComponent should not set bids on service failure
HomeComponent should clear session storage if logging out
HomeComponent should call get bids on product for child component
LoginComponent should set isLoggedIn if new session token was retrieved successfully
LoginComponent should set isLoggedIn if session token is already present during page load
LoginComponent should set isLoginFailed if new session token was not retrieved
ProductViewerComponent should get list of products on page load
ProductViewerComponent should have empty list of products on service failure
ProductViewerComponent should emit selected product event if called
AuthGuardService should pass-through to restricted pages if logged in
AuthGuardService should guard restricted pages if not logged in
